com.TennisApp.java

Class LeagueAssignSearch

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.TennisApp.java.LeagueAssignSearch

  • public class LeagueAssignSearch
extends java.lang.Object
    LeagueAssignSearch is a JavaBean holding LeagueAssignSearch type and League_Assignment data to be used by TennisApp when maintaining League_Assignment records. This is the javabean object that determines if PlayerToLeagueAssignmentServlet.java controller servlet should be returned a League_Assignment result, results, or a message if not found. Created by Dave on 12/12/2015.
